caption.p: MD significantly suppressed the expression levels of HSV-1 proteins. L929 ( a), MEF( b), HeLa( c) and T98G( d) were pretreated with DMSO or MD at indicated concentration for 1 h prior to infection with HSV-1 for additional 6 h. Viral proteins were harvested from cell lysates and the expression levels of gB and ICP6 were detected by western blot analysis
